Package com.wileyedge.fashiontrendanalysis.model

Class Trend

java.lang.Object
com.wileyedge.fashiontrendanalysis.model.Trend
public class Trend extends Object
Represents a fashion trend with various attributes such as name, description, category, designer, etc.

      Constructs a Trend instance with the provided parameters.
      Parameters:
      trendId - The unique identifier for the trend.
      trendName - The name of the trend.
      trendDesc - The description of the trend.
      categoryId - The identifier for the category to which this trend belongs.
      designerId - The identifier for the designer who created this trend.
      location - The location where this trend is popular.
      season - The season during which this trend is popular.
      popularityScore - The score indicating the popularity of this trend.
